originalText.text: Dr. Weintraub went highly recommended to me by a friend and I am so happy I went to him! He is genuinely concerned about his patients and took the time needed to make me feel comfortable and answer all questions. All of the staff have been friendly and the communication has been amazing! My rhinoplasty went well and I even got a phone call the next day to see how I was feeling. I would definitely recommend anyone who wants a great experience with plastic surgery to go here. I drive 45 minutes to an hour each way, and it is worth every minute of that!

originalText.text: I have absolutely been impressed with my care here.  Everything was handled so precisely and professionally. I was 100% satisfied with the results of my rhinoplasty and would recommend anyone who is considering having their nose done to do so here.  Dr. Weintraub is not pushy and doesn't pressure you into having surgery. He listens to your desires and makes the best plan for you. If I ever decide to have any other work done, I will 100% be coming here again.

originalText.text: I cannot say enough good things about my experience with Dr. Weintraub and his staff! As a medical professional working in a surgical specialty, it was clear to me that Dr. Weintraub has an impeccable eye for detail, cares deeply about patient outcomes, and genuinely enjoys what he does. This is reflected not only in his demeanor, but in his team’s as they could not have been kinder or more competent.

originalText.text: When I say Dr Weintraub saved my life I mean it from the  bottom of my heart. No medical professional has ever made me feel like they cared and would fight for my happiness the way he did. Dr Weintraub freed me from issues both functional and emotional and I am overjoyed to put my nose journey behind me and move on with my life. I can’t recommend him enough, if you schedule a consult and meet him I promise you will know instantly you are in the best of hands. Thanks you Dr Barry, you  know how much I adore you!

originalText.text: After a few years of thinking about getting a facelift, I  finally had the surgery  performed by Dr. Weintraub. His office staff is very friendly,  professional and helpful from beginning to end. Dr. Barry explained everything to me step by step and he was very thorough.  He was very accommodating to  my schedule and the results are fantastic. I don’t look “fake”, but these glow and smoothness add me so much more confidence! I  would recommend Dr. Weintraub to perform your specific plastic surgery. He is very patient and has a great bed-side manner !!
